What all required to build software?
- How to write a code?
- How to run a code?
- How to test & debug code
- How to deploy code

All the above things available in IDE (Integrated Development Environment)
Pycharm is IDE. Why Pycharm?
- Beginner friendly
- Free
- Applicable in professional settings

Download Python - python.org > Downloads > latest version (3.12.4)
Download Pycharm - jetbrains.com/pycharm > download community version
ctrl+shift+n - search project
ctrl+g - search line of code in particular project
ctrl+/ - comment out the whole line of code

Git & Github are version control system (VCS)
- it keeps a record
- backups
- make easy collaboration
git-scm.com - website of git